title: Pilot guides Globe Trekker 16 series 13 episodes
description:
Hi,over the past few years I have been collecting the PILOT GUIDES/GLOBE TREKKER series of TV shows.Now I have a huge collection and I want to share with you.I did not rip these series, I only collect them from different sources.
Big thanks to those who did do the ripping and capping.

Please visit this link: <a href="
http://www.pilotguides.com/tv_shows/globe_trekker/shows/series.php" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.pilotguides.com/tv_shows/globe_trekker/shows/series.php</a>

and you will find very helpful Globe Trekker episodes list.Every episode has his originally place and number in this list.At this day list contains 16 series,each series contains 13 episodes.My goal is to present my collection BY SERIES.

And now HERE YOU ARE.SERIES 16 contains:

16.01 Buenos Aires City Guide
16.02 Colonial Australia     **dubbed russian  **
16.03 Art Trails of the Riviera
16.04 Great Australian Hikes
16.05 Myanmar ( Burma )
16.06 World War One Special
16.07 Good and Bad Food Guide 3
16.08 North East England
16.09 Switzerland
16.10 Building England :The Age of Architects
16.11 Delhi and Rajasthan
16.12 Central Japan
16.13 Mumbai City Guide

The episode number 10 is still missing...sorry.

Please help seed once you've finished downloading as these torrents are quite large and my connection isn't the great.
Fill free with any questions or comments.Thank you.
